"```sql\nSELECT \n    SUM(CASE WHEN Currency = 'CZK' THEN Amount ELSE 0 END) AS Total_CZK,\n    SUM(CASE WHEN Currency = 'EUR' THEN Amount ELSE 0 END) AS Total_EUR\nFROM \n    transactions_1k t\nJOIN \n    customers c ON t.CustomerID = c.CustomerID\nWHERE \n    c.Segment = 'SME';\n``` \n\nThis SQL query calculates the total amount paid by SMEs in Czech koruna (CZK) and euros (EUR) by summing the `Amount` column from the `transactions_1k` table, filtered by the `Segment` of the customers in the `customers` table."